1. Avoid Blocking Sleep Calls
    Use always Implicit wait or Explicit wait.

2. Name the Test Cases & Test Suites Appropriately

3. Set the Browser Zoom Level to 100 percent
    driver.execute_script("document.body.style.zoom='100 %'")

4. Maximize the Browser Window
    driver.maximize_window()

5. Choose the Best-Suited Web Locator
    CSS locator >> XPATH locator

6. Implement Logging and Reporting
    Reporting usar allure

7. Use Design Patterns and Principles i.e. Page Object Model (POM)

8. Follow a Uniform Directory Structure

9.  Use Data-Driven Testing for Parameterization
        Usar fixtures.

10. Do Not Use a Single Driver Implementation
        Probar en Crhome y Firefox.

11. Use Assert and Verify in Appropriate Scenarios
        Solo un assert por prueba

12. Avoid Code Duplication
        Usar Wrapping Selenium calls

13. Leverage Parallel Testing in Selenium

